<!DOCTYPE html>

<html lang="ja">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>ジャグラー判別ツール</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Orbitron:wght@400;700;900&family=Noto+Sans+JP:wght@300;400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>

*{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box}
body{background:#0a0a0f;color:#dde0f0;font-family:‘Noto Sans JP’,sans-serif;min-height:100vh;overflow-x:hidden}
body::before{
content:’’;position:fixed;inset:0;pointer-events:none;z-index:0;
background:radial-gradient(ellipse at 15% 15%,rgba(255,61,110,.07) 0%,transparent 55%),
radial-gradient(ellipse at 85% 85%,rgba(0,229,255,.07) 0%,transparent 55%);
}
.wrap{max-width:980px;margin:0 auto;padding:20px 16px 60px;position:relative;z-index:1}

header{text-align:center;padding:36px 0 26px;margin-bottom:28px;border-bottom:1px solid #252535;position:relative}
header::after{
content:’’;position:absolute;bottom:-1px;left:50%;transform:translateX(-50%);
width:240px;height:2px;background:linear-gradient(90deg,transparent,#ff3d6e,#00e5ff,transparent)
}
.logo{
font-family:‘Orbitron’,sans-serif;font-size:clamp(22px,5.5vw,42px);font-weight:900;letter-spacing:.18em;
background:linear-gradient(135deg,#ff3d6e 0%,#ff8c00 40%,#00e5ff 100%);
-webkit-background-clip:text;-webkit-text-fill-color:transparent;background-clip:text
}
.sub{font-size:11px;letter-spacing:.32em;color:#7a7a9a;margin-top:6px;text-transform:uppercase}
.ver{display:inline-block;margin-top:12px;padding:4px 14px;border-radius:20px;border:1px solid rgba(0,229,255,.3);font-size:10px;letter-spacing:.2em;color:#00e5ff;text-transform:uppercase}

.section{background:#111118;border:1px solid #252535;border-radius:14px;padding:22px 24px;margin-bottom:16px;position:relative;overflow:hidden}
.section::before{content:’’;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;right:0;height:2px;background:linear-gradient(90deg,#ff3d6e,#00e5ff);opacity:.45}
.sec-title{font-family:‘Orbitron’,sans-serif;font-size:10px;letter-spacing:.3em;color:#00e5ff;text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:18px}

.mtabs{display:flex;gap:8px;flex-wrap:wrap}
.mtab{background:transparent;border:1px solid #252535;color:#7a7a9a;padding:8px 14px;border-radius:7px;cursor:pointer;font-family:‘Noto Sans JP’,sans-serif;font-size:13px;transition:all .2s}
.mtab:hover{border-color:#ff3d6e;color:#dde0f0}
.mtab.active{background:linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(255,61,110,.18),rgba(0,229,255,.07));border-color:#ff3d6e;color:#ff3d6e;box-shadow:0 0 24px rgba(255,61,110,.45)}

.iblock{margin-bottom:22px}
.iblock-title{font-size:11px;letter-spacing:.18em;margin-bottom:12px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:9px;text-transform:uppercase}
.iblock-title::before{content:’’;display:inline-block;width:3px;height:15px;border-radius:2px;flex-shrink:0}
.iblock-title.req{color:#ffd700}.iblock-title.req::before{background:#ffd700}
.iblock-title.opt{color:#7a7a9a}.iblock-title.opt::before{background:#5a5a7a}
.badge-opt{margin-left:4px;padding:1px 7px;border-radius:4px;background:rgba(255,255,255,.06);font-size:9px;letter-spacing:.1em;color:#5a5a7a}

.igrid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fill,minmax(155px,1fr));gap:12px}
.igroup{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:6px}
label{font-size:11px;color:#7a7a9a;letter-spacing:.05em}
.hint{font-size:10px;color:rgba(100,100,140,.65);margin-top:1px;line-height:1.4}

input[type=number]{
background:rgba(255,255,255,.04);border:1px solid #252535;border-radius:8px;
color:#dde0f0;padding:10px 12px;font-size:15px;font-family:‘Orbitron’,sans-serif;
font-weight:700;width:100%;transition:all .2s;-moz-appearance:textfield
}
input[type=number]::-webkit-inner-spin-button,input[type=number]::-webkit-outer-spin-button{-webkit-appearance:none}
input[type=number]:focus{outline:none;border-color:#00e5ff;box-shadow:0 0 24px rgba(0,229,255,.35);background:rgba(0,229,255,.04)}
input.opt{border-style:dashed}

.divider{height:1px;background:#1e1e2e;margin:18px 0}

.cbtn{
display:block;width:100%;padding:17px;border:none;border-radius:11px;
background:linear-gradient(135deg,#ff3d6e,#ff7a00);color:#fff;
font-family:‘Orbitron’,sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.22em;
cursor:pointer;transition:all .2s;text-transform:uppercase;
box-shadow:0 4px 22px rgba(255,61,110,.45);margin-top:6px
}
.cbtn:hover{transform:translateY(-2px);box-shadow:0 8px 32px rgba(255,61,110,.65)}
.cbtn:active{transform:translateY(0)}
.footnote{font-size:10px;color:#5a5a7a;text-align:center;margin-top:8px;opacity:.65;line-height:1.7}

#result{display:none}

.srow{display:flex;gap:10px;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-bottom:20px}
.scard{flex:1;min-width:105px;background:rgba(255,255,255,.03);border:1px solid #252535;border-radius:10px;padding:13px;text-align:center}
.slabel{font-size:9px;color:#7a7a9a;letter-spacing:.1em;margin-bottom:5px;text-transform:uppercase}
.sval{font-family:‘Orbitron’,sans-serif;font-size:16px;font-weight:700;color:#00e5ff}
.snote{font-size:9px;color:#5a5a7a;margin-top:3px}

.conf-wrap{margin-bottom:22px}
.conf-head{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;margin-bottom:8px}
.conf-lbl{font-size:10px;color:#7a7a9a;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase}
.conf-pct{font-family:‘Orbitron’,sans-serif;font-size:13px;font-weight:700}
.conf-bar{height:8px;background:rgba(255,255,255,.06);border-radius:4px;overflow:hidden}
.conf-fill{height:100%;border-radius:4px;width:0%;transition:width 1.1s cubic-bezier(.16,1,.3,1);background:linear-gradient(90deg,#ff3d6e,#ffd700,#00ff88)}
.conf-note{font-size:10px;color:#5a5a7a;margin-top:6px}

.bars{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:10px}
.brow{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px}
.blabel{font-family:‘Orbitron’,sans-serif;font-size:10px;width:54px;flex-shrink:0;color:#7a7a9a}
.blabel b{font-size:17px;font-weight:700}
.btrack{flex:1;height:28px;background:rgba(255,255,255,.04);border-radius:7px;overflow:hidden;border:1px solid #252535}
.bfill{height:100%;border-radius:7px;width:0%;transition:width .95s cubic-bezier(.16,1,.3,1);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:flex-end;padding-right:10px}
.bpct{font-family:‘Orbitron’,sans-serif;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;color:rgba(0,0,0,.85);white-space:nowrap}

.bdwrap{margin-top:18px;padding:16px 18px;background:rgba(255,255,255,.02);border:1px solid #252535;border-radius:11px}
.bdtitle{font-size:10px;color:#7a7a9a;letter-spacing:.2em;text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:14px}
.bdgrid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fill,minmax(130px,1fr));gap:8px}
.bditem{background:rgba(255,255,255,.03);border:1px solid #252535;border-radius:8px;padding:10px 8px;text-align:center}
.bdfactor{font-size:9px;color:#7a7a9a;letter-spacing:.1em;margin-bottom:4px;text-transform:uppercase}
.bdobs{font-family:‘Orbitron’,sans-serif;font-size:13px;font-weight:700;color:#dde0f0}
.bdexp{font-size:9px;color:#5a5a7a;margin-top:2px}
.bddiff{font-size:10px;font-weight:700;margin-top:3px}
.ok{color:#00ff88}.warn{color:#ffd700}.bad{color:#ff3d6e}

.verdict{margin-top:18px;padding:18px 22px;border-radius:11px;text-align:center}
.verdict.high{background:linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(0,255,136,.09),rgba(0,229,255,.07));border:1px solid rgba(0,255,136,.35)}
.verdict.mid{background:linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(255,215,0,.08),rgba(255,100,0,.06));border:1px solid rgba(255,215,0,.3)}
.verdict.low{background:rgba(255,255,255,.02);border:1px solid #252535}
.vt{font-family:‘Orbitron’,sans-serif;font-size:14px;letter-spacing:.1em;margin-bottom:9px}
.vb{font-size:12px;color:#7a7a9a;line-height:1.9}

.evwrap{margin-top:18px;padding:16px 18px;background:rgba(255,255,255,.02);border:1px solid #252535;border-radius:11px}
.evtitle{font-size:10px;color:#7a7a9a;letter-spacing:.2em;text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:14px}
.evgrid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(6,1fr);gap:8px}
.evcard{background:rgba(255,255,255,.03);border:1px solid #252535;border-radius:8px;padding:11px 6px;text-align:center}
.evcard.top{border-color:#ff3d6e;background:rgba(255,61,110,.09)}
.evs{font-family:‘Orbitron’,sans-serif;font-size:10px;color:#7a7a9a;margin-bottom:4px}
.evn{font-family:‘Orbitron’,sans-serif;font-size:13px;font-weight:700}
.evn.p{color:#00ff88}.evn.n{color:#ff3d6e}
.evl{font-size:9px;color:#5a5a7a;margin-top:2px}
.evp{font-size:11px;color:#00e5ff;margin-top:5px;font-weight:700}

.rbtn{background:transparent;border:1px solid #252535;color:#7a7a9a;padding:11px 20px;border-radius:8px;cursor:pointer;font-family:‘Noto Sans JP’,sans-serif;font-size:13px;margin-top:18px;transition:all .2s;width:100%}
.rbtn:hover{border-color:#ff3d6e;color:#dde0f0}

.caution-box{
display:flex;gap:12px;align-items:flex-start;
margin-top:14px;padding:12px 16px;
background:rgba(255,215,0,.06);
border:1px solid rgba(255,215,0,.3);
border-radius:10px;
}
.caution-icon{font-size:18px;flex-shrink:0;margin-top:1px}
.caution-text{font-size:11px;color:#7a7a9a;line-height:1.9}
.caution-text strong{color:#ffd700;letter-spacing:.05em}
.caution-hi{color:#ffd700;font-weight:700}

.ptabs{display:flex;gap:8px;margin-bottom:16px}
.ptab{
flex:1;padding:11px 0;border-radius:10px;border:1px solid #252535;
background:transparent;color:#7a7a9a;cursor:pointer;
font-family:‘Noto Sans JP’,sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-weight:700;
letter-spacing:.08em;transition:all .2s;
}
.ptab:hover{border-color:#00e5ff;color:#dde0f0}
.ptab.active{
background:linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(0,229,255,.15),rgba(255,61,110,.08));
border-color:#00e5ff;color:#00e5ff;
box-shadow:0 0 24px rgba(0,229,255,.35);
}

.gp-row{display:grid;grid-template-columns:52px 130px 1fr 130px;gap:8px;align-items:center;margin-bottom:10px}
.gp-slabel{font-weight:700;font-size:13px}
.gp-theory{font-size:11px;color:#7a7a9a}
.gp-track{height:8px;background:#252535;border-radius:4px;overflow:hidden}
.gp-fill{height:100%;border-radius:4px;transition:width .5s ease}
.gp-diff{font-size:11px;text-align:right}
.gp-ok{color:#00ff88}
.gp-hi{color:#00e5ff}
.gp-lo{color:#7a7a9a}
.gp-top{background:rgba(255,61,110,.08);border:1px solid rgba(255,61,110,.3);border-radius:8px;padding:6px 8px}

@media(max-width:600px){
.gp-row{grid-template-columns:44px 110px 1fr 100px;font-size:10px}
}

@keyframes fadeUp{from{opacity:0;transform:translateY(12px)}to{opacity:1;transform:translateY(0)}}
.anim{animation:fadeUp .4s ease forwards}

@media(max-width:600px){
.evgrid{grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr)}
.igrid{grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr}
.bdgrid{grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr}
.scard{min-width:calc(50% - 10px)}
}

/* === スマホ向けレイアウト改善 === */
.wrap{max-width:520px;padding:12px 12px 60px}
.section{padding:14px 14px;margin-bottom:10px}
.iblock{margin-bottom:12px}
.iblock-title{margin-bottom:7px}
.igrid{grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:8px}
input[type=number]{font-size:16px;padding:11px 10px;min-height:46px;border-radius:10px;background:rgba(255,255,255,.06)}
label{font-size:12px}
.hint{font-size:10px}
.divider{margin:10px 0}
.cbtn{padding:15px;font-size:13px;letter-spacing:.12em;border-radius:12px;margin-top:4px}
.ptab{font-size:15px;padding:13px 0}
.caution-box{padding:8px 11px;margin-top:8px}
.caution-text{font-size:10px;line-height:1.7}
.footnote{font-size:10px;margin-top:5px}
.sticky-btn{position:sticky;bottom:0;z-index:50;padding:8px 0;background:linear-gradient(0deg,#0a0a0f 65%,transparent 100%)}
@media(max-width:600px){
.srow{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:8px}
.scard{min-width:0;flex:unset}
.evgrid{grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr)}
.bdgrid{grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr}
.gp-row{grid-template-columns:42px 1fr 82px;font-size:10px}
}

/* Safari select強制スタイル */
select {
background-color: #1a1a2e !important;
color: #dde0f0 !important;
-webkit-text-fill-color: #dde0f0 !important;
border: 1px solid #252535 !important;
border-radius: 10px !important;
padding: 13px 14px !important;
font-size: 15px !important;
font-weight: 700 !important;
-webkit-appearance: none !important;
appearance: none !important;
}
select option {
background-color: #111118;
color: #dde0f0;
}
</style>

</head>
<body>
<div class="wrap">

<header>
  <div class="logo">ジャグラー判別ツール</div>
  <div class="sub">設定判別 &amp; 期待値計算システム</div>
  <div class="ver">▸ 多次元ベイズ推定 Ver 2.2</div>
</header>

<!-- ページタブ -->

<div class="ptabs">
  <button class="ptab active" onclick="switchPage('analyzer',this)">⚙ 設定判別</button>
  <button class="ptab" onclick="switchPage('grape',this)">🍇 ぶどう逆算</button>
</div>

<!-- ========== 設定判別ページ ========== -->

<div id="page-analyzer" style="display:block">

  <!-- 機種選択 -->

  <div class="section">
    <div class="sec-title">▸ 機種選択</div>
    <select id="machine-select" onchange="selMDropdown(this.value)" style="width:100%;padding:13px 14px;border-radius:10px;background:#1a1a2e;border:1px solid #252535;color:#dde0f0;font-family:'Noto Sans JP',sans-serif;font-size:15px;font-weight:700;cursor:pointer;-webkit-appearance:none;appearance:none;-webkit-text-fill-color:#dde0f0">
      <option value="aime">アイムジャグラーEX-TP</option>
      <option value="neo">ネオアイムジャグラーEX</option>
      <option value="gogo3">ゴーゴージャグラー3</option>
      <option value="my5">マイジャグラー5</option>
      <option value="funky2">ファンキージャグラー2</option>
      <option value="happyv3">ハッピージャグラーV3</option>
      <option value="girlsss">ジャグラーガールズSS</option>
      <option value="mr">ミスタージャグラー</option>
      <option value="ultra">ウルトラミラクルジャグラー</option>
    </select>>
    <div id="estimated-note" style="display:none;margin-top:12px;padding:10px 14px;border-radius:8px;background:rgba(255,200,0,.08);border:1px solid rgba(255,200,0,.25);font-size:11px;color:#ffd700;line-height:1.6;"></div>
  </div>

  <!-- データ入力 -->

  <div class="section">
    <div class="sec-title">▸ データ入力</div>

<div class="iblock">
  <div class="iblock-title req">基本データ（必須）</div>
  <div class="igrid">
    <div class="igroup">
      <label>総ゲーム数</label>
      <input type="number" id="games" placeholder="例: 3000" min="0">
    </div>
    <div class="igroup">
      <label>BIG 合計回数</label>
      <input type="number" id="big" placeholder="例: 15" min="0">
    </div>
    <div class="igroup">
      <label>REG 合計回数</label>
      <input type="number" id="reg" placeholder="例: 18" min="0">
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="divider"></div>

<div class="iblock">
  <div class="iblock-title opt">ボーナス内訳 <span class="badge-opt">入力で精度UP</span></div>
  <div class="igrid">
    <div class="igroup">
      <label id="label-bigS">単独 BIG</label>
      <input type="number" id="bigS" placeholder="空欄=未入力" min="0" class="opt">
      <div class="hint" id="hint-bigS">左リールにチェリーが止まらずペカった BIG</div>
    </div>
    <div class="igroup">
      <label>チェリー重複 BIG</label>
      <input type="number" id="bigC" placeholder="空欄=未入力" min="0" class="opt">
      <div class="hint">左リールにチェリーが止まりペカった BIG</div>
    </div>
    <div class="igroup">
      <label>単独 REG</label>
      <input type="number" id="regS" placeholder="空欄=未入力" min="0" class="opt">
      <div class="hint">左リールにチェリーが止まらずペカった REG</div>
    </div>
    <div class="igroup">
      <label>チェリー重複 REG</label>
      <input type="number" id="regC" placeholder="空欄=未入力" min="0" class="opt">
      <div class="hint">左リールにチェリーが止まりペカった REG</div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="caution-box">
    <div class="caution-icon">⚠️</div>
    <div class="caution-text">
      ハッピージャグラー・ミスタージャグラー以外はボーナス優先制御なので、左リールに7が停止してペカった場合、<span class="caution-hi">単独ボーナスかチェリー重複ボーナスか判別できません。</span><br>
      正確にカウントするには、常に<span class="caution-hi">左リールにチェリー狙い（枠上〜上段にBAR目押し）</span>する必要があります。
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="divider"></div>

<div class="iblock">
  <div class="iblock-title opt">小役カウント <span class="badge-opt">入力で精度UP</span></div>
  <div class="igrid">
    <div class="igroup">
      <label>ぶどう回数</label>
      <input type="number" id="grape" placeholder="空欄=未入力" min="0" class="opt">
      <div class="hint">ボーナス中を除いた通常時のみの回数</div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div style="margin-top:10px;font-size:10px;color:#7a7a9a;line-height:1.7">
    💡 チェリー重複BIG・REGを正確にカウントすることで判別精度が大きく上がります
  </div>
</div>

<div class="sticky-btn"><button class="cbtn" onclick="analyze()">▶ 設定を解析する</button></div>
<p class="footnote">
  ※ボーナス内訳・小役は入力しなくても解析できます。入れるほど精度が上がります！<br>
  ※ぶどうはボーナス中を除いた通常時のみカウントしてください。
</p>

  </div>

  <!-- 解析結果 -->

  <div class="section" id="result" style="display:none">
    <div class="sec-title">▸ 解析結果</div>
    <div class="srow" id="srow"></div>
    <div class="conf-wrap">
      <div class="conf-head">
        <span class="conf-lbl">▸ 解析信頼度スコア</span>
        <span class="conf-pct" id="confPct">—</span>
      </div>
      <div class="conf-bar"><div class="conf-fill" id="confFill"></div></div>
      <div class="conf-note" id="confNote"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="bars" id="bars"></div>
    <div class="bdwrap" id="bdwrap"></div>
    <div class="verdict" id="verdict"></div>
    <div class="evwrap">
      <div class="evtitle">▸ 設定別 期待収支（20スロ 46枚 21.74円／4,000G 等価計算）＆ 推定設定確率</div>
      <div class="evgrid" id="evgrid"></div>
    </div>

<!-- AI相談セクション -->

<div style="margin-top:24px;border-top:1px solid #252535;padding-top:20px">
  <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;margin-bottom:14px">
    <span style="font-family:Orbitron,sans-serif;font-size:10px;letter-spacing:.25em;color:#00e5ff">▸ AI スロプロ相談</span>
    <span style="font-size:10px;color:#5a5a7a;padding:2px 8px;border:1px solid #252535;border-radius:4px">解析データを自動読取</span>
  </div>
  <div id="ai-apikey-wrap" style="display:none;margin-bottom:12px;padding:12px 14px;background:rgba(0,200,100,.06);border:1px solid rgba(0,200,100,.2);border-radius:8px">
    <div style="font-size:11px;color:#00e5a0;margin-bottom:8px">🔑 Gemini API キーを入力してください（無料）</div>
    <div style="display:flex;gap:8px">
